A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta ba da shawarar sabon coronavirus a matsayin mai daukar hoto, wanda yanzu ake kira SARS-CoV-2.
An kira shi cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) saboda cutar ta haifar da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Shaidar da aka samu ya nuna cewa kashi 80% na mutanen da ke fama da COVID-19 suna da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi, wato, cututtukan numfashi tare da ko ba tare da cutar huhu ba kuma yawancin su sun warke.
A cikin kashi 14 cikin dari na masu cutar COVID-19 suna da mummunan ciwo wanda ke buƙatar asibiti, yayin da kashi 6 cikin dari na marasa lafiya ke da mummunan ciwo wanda ke buƙatar magani mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke kwance a asibiti saboda COVID-19 ya kai kashi 4 cikin dari.
A cikin wannan binciken, mun kimanta yanayin haɗuwa na COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a cikin EU/EEA da United Kingdom (UK) kuma mun kwatanta su da lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Bayan China, COVID-19 ya kara yaduwa a duniya kuma sauran ƙasashen duniya yanzu suna bin yanayin COVID-19 a cikin ƙasar.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin fitowar EuroSurveillance 2020, Spiteri et al na 5 ga Maris, WHO ta ba da rahoton farkon yanayin COVID-19 a Turai kamar yadda ta bayyana.
A cikin EU/EEA, Faransa ta sanar da farko uku tabbatacce lokuta dawo daga Wuhan, lardin Hubei na kasar Sin a ranar 24 ga Janairu, 2020.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano shari'o'in COVID-19 a duk ƙasashen EU/EEA 30 da Ingila (UK), tare da ba da rahoton shari'o'i 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727 a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, tare da shari'o'i 17,750 da mutuwar 1,441 a Italiya kadai.
Samun adadin adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da kuma yawan abubuwan da suka faru.
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana yin rikodin shari'ar COVID-19 ta kowace ƙasa a duniya, wanda ake sabunta bayanai a kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe ta amfani da ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da kuma tushen hukuma kamar WHO.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanan don tantance yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK da kwatanta su da shari'o'in a Italiya.
A matsayin samfurin yanayin yanayin COVID-19 mai aiki, mun lissafa jimlar kwanaki 14 na COVID-19 na lokuta, muna la'akari da yanayin yaduwar COVID-19 a kowace EU/EEA da Burtaniya a cikin lokacin Janairu 1 - 15 Maris 2020.
Mun kuma gabatar da adadin adadin wadanda aka ruwaito a kowace kasa da karfe 8:00 na safe a ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020 kuma mun kwatanta su da adadin wadanda aka ruwaito a Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK
Tsarin gabaɗaya na kwanaki 14 na rarrabuwar kawunan COVID-19 a cikin ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK yayi kama da na lardin Hubei (China) (Figure 1).
A cikin EU/EEA gabaɗaya da UK, haɗuwa da shari'ar COVID-19 ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu sannan ya fara ƙaruwa da sauri a kusan 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (abun da aka ƙara).
Wannan ya hada da yawan adadin wadanda aka ruwaito a cikin Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da UK suna nuna irin wannan yanayin na haɓaka na COVID-19 (abun da aka ƙara).
Figure 2 ya nuna yawan adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK idan aka kwatanta da adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Ya nuna cewa a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8 na safe, an riga an samu adadin adadin masu cutar a cikin wasu kasashe 15 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya kamar yadda Italiya ta samu makonni 3 da suka gabata ko kuma ƙasa da haka.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana karuwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Halin da aka lura a cikin hadadden lokuta na COVID-19 ya nuna cewa annobar tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a cikin ƙasashe.
Bugu da kari, yayin da kasashe daban-daban ke cikin matakai daban-daban, bambance-bambance tsakanin martani na lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa da yiwuwar bambance-bambance tsakanin ƙasashe da kuma zaɓin haƙuri daban-daban ya kamata a bincika don tabbatar da COVID-19, gami da gwajin kama-da-wane.
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun bayyana halin da ake ciki wanda ke buƙatar kulawar ICU don kashi 10% na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun nuna cewa asibitoci da cibiyoyin kula da marasa lafiya a waɗannan yankuna sun riga sun kai iyakar ƙarfin su.
Bayanai game da shigar da marasa lafiya na COVID-19 asibiti da/ko cibiyoyin kulawa na musamman a halin yanzu ana samun su ne kawai don kashi 6% da 1% na shari'o'i a matakin EU/EEA, bi da bi (ba a nuna bayanai ba).
Amma suna buƙatar tattara bayanan sa ido na yanzu ta hanyar da ta dace wanda ke mai da hankali kan adadin adadin rahotannin da aka bayar da rahoton da kuma yawan mutuwar.
Wani binciken da aka yi a 2010-11 ya nuna cewa akwai bambanci sosai tsakanin yawan gadajen kula da marasa lafiya a Turai, wanda ya kai gado 29.2 a Jamus da 4.2 a Portugal a kowace jama'a 100,000.
Wannan yana nufin cewa wasu ƙasashe suna da ƙasa ko fiye da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (akuwa 12.5 na ICU da gadajen kulawa na matsakaici a cikin 2010-11 ga kowane mutum 100,000).
Yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 da aka kwantar a asibiti a kowace EU/EEA da Burtaniya yanayin samfurin da ke da alaƙa da wadatar ƙarfin kiwon lafiya yana da alaƙa da haɗarin wucewa > 90% na ƙarfin gado mai mahimmanci, wanda aka bayar a cikin sabuntawa na shida na ECDC Rapid Risk Assessment of COVID-19.
Tun da har yanzu an iyakance adadin masu cutar ga wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa da gaggawa suna ba da magani ga wasu yankuna, ya kamata a samar da bayanan shari'o'i da cibiyoyin kula da gaggawa a cikin ma'anar cibiyoyin yanki don ƙididdigar 2 (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da halin da ake ciki a wasu ƙasashe ya nuna cewa cutar COVID-19 tana yaduwa cikin sauri a cikin EU/EEA da UK.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da cibiyoyin kulawa na musamman suna buƙatar shirya kansu don ci gaba da kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2 a cikin al'umma da kuma yawan marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 waɗanda ke buƙatar kula da kiwon lafiya da kuma musamman kulawar kulawa ta musamman, kamar yadda yanayin ya kasance a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
A cewar sabon tsarin hadarin ECDC, gaggawa, aiki da kuma cikakkiyar hanyar kawar da cutar SARS-CoV-2 tana da mahimmanci maimakon jinkirta hana yaduwar cutar, saboda idan ba a aiwatar da shi ba da wuri, saurin karuwar irin waɗannan shari'o'in ba zai ba masu yanke shawara da asibitoci damar fahimtar, karɓa da kuma karɓar martani ba.
Har ila yau, an lissafa matakan kiwon lafiyar jama'a a cikin saurin kimanta haɗarin don kawar da tasirin cutar.
Akwai ɗan gajeren lokaci na dama a nan lokacin da ƙasashe za su iya ƙara haɓaka ƙoƙarin su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage matsin lamba kan ayyukan kiwon lafiya.
Idan wannan ya gaza, akwai yiwuwar sauran tsarin kiwon lafiya na EU/EEA na iya fuskantar karuwar marasa lafiya da ke buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa.
Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19) ta barke ne sakamakon mummunar cutar numfashi mai saurin kamuwa da cuta (SARS) Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) wanda ya riga ya kashe mutane sama da 3,000 da kuma kamuwa da mutane sama da 80,000 a China da sauran wurare a duniya, kuma ya zama bala'i ga bil'adama.
Kamar SARS-CoV, wanda ya haifar da cutar SARS a cikin shekara ta 2003, SARS-CoV-2 mai yiwuwa ya kamu da cutar daga ƙuda kuma yana nuna alamun bayyanar cututtuka ta hanyar wannan hanyar.
Ko da yake cutar COVID-19 tana da rauni da mutuwar mutane fiye da SARS, amma tana da kamuwa da cuta kuma tana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa da maza fiye da mata.
A cikin martani ga yawan wallafe-wallafen da ke faruwa a cikin cututtukan da ke faruwa, wannan labarin yana ƙoƙari ya ba da cikakken bayani game da batun bincike da ke faruwa.
Mun magance abubuwan yau da kullun kamar ilimin annoba, ilimin halittu, ilimin kwayar cuta, ganewar asali, magani, tsinkaya da rigakafin cutar.
Ko da yake akwai tambayoyi da yawa da ba a amsa ba, muna fatan wannan bita zai taimaka wajen fahimtar wannan cuta mai haɗari da kuma magance ta.
Bikin bazara na ranar 25 ga Janairu, 2020 ya kasance abin ban mamaki da ba za a iya mantawa da shi ba ga duk Sinawa waɗanda aka umarce su da su zauna a gida a duk lokacin hutu da kuma makonni da yawa bayan barkewar sabuwar cutar.
Wannan kwayar cutar tana da alaƙa da kwayar cutar coronavirus (CoV) wacce ta haifar da barkewar cutar saurin kamuwa da cutar numfashi (SARS) a 2003, don haka a ranar 11 ga Fabrairun 2020, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sake sanya mata suna SARS-CoV-2 da kuma cutar da ke tattare da ita COV Disease 19 (COVID-19).
Cutar ta fara ne a Wuhan, China kuma nan take ta bazu zuwa duk fadin kasar da kuma wasu kasashe 50 a duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, kwayar cutar ta haifar da tabbataccen shari'o'in COVID-19 80,000, tare da sakin marasa lafiya sama da 40,000 da mutuwar marasa lafiya 3,000.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "maƙiyi na farko na mutane" ne kuma mai yiwuwa ya fi ta'addanci ƙarfi.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), an buga sama da takardu 200 kan COVID-19 a cikin watanni biyu da suka gabata, wanda ya haɗa da ilimin kwayoyin cuta, ilimin annoba, ilimin halittu, ganewar asali da magani tun lokacin da aka fara rahoton shari'ar farko a ranar 7 ga Janairu, 2020, wanda ya ba da damar tsara jerin cututtukan cutar ban da marasa lafiya daban-daban.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙari ya taƙaita ci gaban bincike a cikin sababbin fannoni masu tasowa.
Idan za mu iya, za mu yi ƙoƙarin kwatanta COVID-19 da SARS da sauran cututtukan da ke haifar da CoV, cututtukan numfashi na Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS, barkewar 2012).
Za mu kuma tattauna abin da muka koya game da rigakafin cututtuka da kuma tsinkayar su, da kuma wasu batutuwa masu muhimmanci da suka rage.
CoVs a al'adance ana ɗaukar su marasa cutarwa ga ɗan adam, suna haifar da kusan 15% na cututtukan mura.
Amma a wannan karni mun fuskanci mummunar cutar CoV guda biyu da ke kashe mutane, wato SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, wanda ya fara bulla a China a 2003 da Saudiyya a 2012 kuma nan da nan ya yadu zuwa wasu ƙasashe tare da mummunan cututtuka da mutuwar mutane.
Don haka, COVID-19 na yanzu shine barkewar CoV na uku a tarihin ɗan adam.
