Manyan abubuwan haɗari guda uku don COVID-19 sune jinsi (maza), shekaru (> 60), da kuma cutar nimoniya mai tsanani.
CoVs babban ƙananan ƙwayoyin cuta ne da ke ɗauke da zaren RNA guda ɗaya.
Ana iya raba su zuwa kwayoyin halittar guda hudu, wato alpha, beta, gamma da delta, daga cikinsu an san alpha- da beta CoVs suna shafar mutane.
Wannan spike mai rufi (S) glycoprotein yana ɗaure da masu karɓar salula na angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) da diapeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) don SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV, bi da bi, sannan kuma ya haifar da haɗuwa da fata.
Ana sakin kwayoyin RNA masu kamuwa da cuta a cikin kwayar halitta; bayan kwayar cutar ta kwayar halitta ta kwayar halitta ta kwayar halitta ta RNA ta samar da kwayar halitta mai dauke da kwayar halitta tare da glycoproteins da nucleocapsid proteins, wanda daga bisani ya hada da membrane plasma don sakin kwayar cutar.
