Shin dole ne a keɓe mutum na kwanaki 24?
Zazzabi shine babban alama da farkon bayyanar COVID-19, wanda zai iya kasancewa ba tare da alamomi ba ko wasu alamomi kamar bushewar tari, tashin zuciya, jijiyoyin jiki, zazzaɓi, ciwon kai, ciwon makogwaro, rhinorrhea, ciwon kirji, zawo, tashin zuciya da amai.
Wasu marasa lafiya na iya samun dyspnea da/ko hypoxemia mako guda bayan kamuwa da cutar.
A cikin mawuyacin hali, marasa lafiya suna da saurin kamuwa da cututtukan numfashi, harin septic, acidosis na rayuwa da kuma coagulopathy.
Masu fama da zazzabi da / ko cututtukan numfashi da zazzabi mai tsanani suna buƙatar gwajin kwayar cutar don ganewar asali, koda kuwa ba a san su ba.
Wani binciken alƙaluma da aka yi a ƙarshen Disamba 2019 ya nuna cewa kashi 98 cikin ɗari na alamun cutar zazzabi ne, kashi 76 cikin ɗari na tari mai bushewa, kashi 55 cikin ɗari na dyspnea da kashi 3 cikin ɗari na zawo; kashi 8 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya suna buƙatar taimakon iska.
Bincike biyu na kwanan nan da aka yi kan wani rukuni na mutane da ke da alaƙa da cutar da kuma wanda ba shi da alamun cutar sun nuna irin wannan binciken.
A kwatankwacin haka, binciken alƙaluma na 2012 ya nuna cewa marasa lafiyar MERS-CoV suma suna da zazzabi (98%), tari mai bushewa (47%) da dyspnea (55%) a matsayin manyan alamun bayyanar cututtuka.
Amma, kashi 80% daga cikinsu sun buƙaci taimakon iska, wanda ya fi na marasa lafiya na COVID-19 yawa kuma MERS ya fi na COVID-19 kisa.
Hakanan an gano zazzabi (26%) da ciwon makogwaro (21%) a cikin marasa lafiyar MERS.
A cikin marasa lafiyar SARS, an gano cewa zazzabi (99%-100%), tari mai bushewa (29%-75%), dyspnea (40%-42%), zawo (20-25%) da ciwon makogwaro (13-25%) sune manyan alamun bayyanar cututtuka, kuma kusan 14%-20% na marasa lafiyar suna buƙatar tallafin iska.
