Gano SARS-CoV-2 RNA ta hanyar juyawa-fassarar polymerase chain reaction (RT-PCR) an yi amfani da shi azaman babban ma'auni don gano COVID-19.
Duk da haka, saboda yawan ƙarancin ƙarancin cutar, an fara amfani da bayyanar cututtuka don ganewar asali a China a ranar 13 ga Fabrairu, 2020 (wanda ba ya dogara da RT-PCR kawai).
