Don haka, haɗuwa da tarihin cutar, bayyanar cututtuka, gwaje-gwajen dakin gwaje-gwaje da binciken radiological suna da mahimmanci kuma suna da mahimmanci don ingantaccen bincike.
A ranar 14 ga Fabrairun 2020, ƙungiyar Feng Zhang ta bayyana wata yarjejeniya ta amfani da fasahar CRISPR-based SHERLOCK don gano SARS-CoV-2, wanda ke gano zaren SARS-CoV-2 na roba a cikin awa ɗaya ba tare da buƙatar kayan aiki masu yawa ba daga 20 × 10-18 mol/L zuwa 200 × 10-18 mol/L (kwafin 10-100 a kowace microliter na shigarwar).
