An gano cewa kawai kashi 87 cikin ɗari na jerin nucleotide sun kasance daidai tsakanin MERS-CoV da bat COVID-HKU25, wanda ke da alaƙa da shi.
Saboda haka, ƙila ba za a iya cewa waɗannan jemage ba masu kula da MERS-CoV ba.
A gefe guda kuma, binciken da aka yi a Gabas ta Tsakiya ya nuna cewa raƙuman Dromedary suna da ƙwayar cuta ga ƙwayoyin cuta na MERS-CoV, kamar raƙuman Gabas ta Tsakiya da aka samu a ƙasashen Afirka da yawa.
