A cikin rikice-rikice na gaskiya, RBD na SARS-CoV-2 da RATG13 sun bambanta, duk da haka, mafi girman adadin kwayoyin halitta suna da babban adadin daidaito.
Binciken da aka yi kwanan nan kan marasa lafiya na pangolins ya kuma ba da rahoton gano wani kwayar cutar a cikin samfurin huhu, wanda aka gano yana da alaƙa da SARS-CoV-2.
Wannan binciken ya ɗauki hanyar haɗuwa ta daban da kuma maganin jiki don samar da jerin kwayoyin halittar ɗan adam kusan kashi 86.3% na cikakken kwayar cutar.
