A matsayin mai motsa juyin halitta, sake haɗuwa ya zama ruwan dare gama gari a cikin beta-CoV.
Har yanzu, juri'a na ci gaba da bincike kan asalin dabbobi na SARS-CoV-2.
Duk da yawan cutar HCoV, an kuma yi nazarin asalin dabbobi na HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-NL63 da HCoV-HKU1.
Shaidar ilimin halittar jini ta nuna cewa HCoV-NL63 da HCoV-229E duka sun samo asali ne daga COVID na kifi, yayin da HCoV-OC43 da HCoV-HKU1 suka samo asali ne daga ƙwari.
An bayar da rahoton cewa cutar COVID a cikin jemage ta ARCOV.2 (Appalachian Ridge COVID) da aka gano a cikin jemage na Arewacin Amurka, yana nuna alaƙa da HCOV-NL63.
A gefe guda, HCoV-229E yana da alaƙa da kwayar halitta a cikin wani kwayar cutar COVID ta bat, wanda aka kira Hipposiderosis/Ghanaquam/19/2008, wanda aka gano a Ghana, a lokacin da aka yi zargin raƙuma a matsayin masu kula da su.
Don ƙarin haske, an ba da taƙaitaccen ilimin yanzu game da asalin dabbobi na HCoV da aka sani a cikin Figure 1 da Table 2.
A tarihi, an gabatar da hujjojin yaduwar HCoV tsakanin jinsuna ta hanyar nazarin tarihin.
Lokacin da HCoV-OC43 ya wuce jinsuna daga dabbobin gida zuwa mutane a cikin shekarun 1890, an rubuta annoba ta kamuwa da cututtukan numfashi.
Tarihin yaduwar HCoV-229E tsakanin jinsuna ba shi da kyau.
An gano cutar ta Bat Alpha-CoV, wacce ke da alaƙa da HCoV-229E.
Ɗaya daga cikinsu yana ɗauke da cutar alpha-CoV.
Akwai shaidu da yawa da ke tallafawa watsa kwayar cutar kai tsaye daga jemage zuwa mutum.
Na farko, yana yiwuwa cewa alpacas ba mutane ba ne suka haɗu da waɗannan dabbobi a cikin yanayin da suke ciki.
Maimakon haka, mutane suna da dangantaka ta kusa da alpacas.
Na biyu, cutar HCoV-229E ta Alpha-CoV ta banbanta da kuma rashin cutarwa a cikin bat, yayin da cutar Alpacus Alpha-CoV ta haifar da cutar numfashi a cikin dabbobi masu cutar.
A ƙarshe, ba a taɓa samun cutar alpacus alpha-CoV a cikin namun daji ba.
Don haka, ba za a iya kawar da yiwuwar cewa alpacas sun sami HCoV-229E-related alpha-CoV daga mutane ba.
A zahiri, jemage sune tushen kai tsaye na ƙwayoyin cuta na ɗan adam, gami da cutar tafin kafa, cutar Ebola, cutar Nipah da cutar Hendra.
Saboda haka, ba abin mamaki ba ne cewa waɗannan jemage suna iya yaɗa HCoV-229E kai tsaye ga mutane.
A madadin haka, bat alpha-CoV shine asalin HCoV-229E, alpacas da dromedary raƙuma na iya zama matsakaici don watsa kwayar cutar ga mutane, kamar yadda ya faru da MERS-CoV.
MERS-CoV ya zama mafi kyawun misali na yaduwar jinsuna daga gizo-gizo zuwa raƙuman dromedary da kuma daga raƙuman dromedary zuwa mutane.
Asalin juyin halitta na MERS-CoV daga kuraje sananne ne saboda asalinsa kuma an ƙarfafa shi ta binciken da aka yi a baya.
A bayyane yake cewa waɗannan jemage suna samar da wadataccen adadi na ƙwayoyin cuta don musayar ƙwayoyin cuta da kuma musayar ƙwayoyin cuta tsakanin jinsuna.
Rayuwa mai tsawo, yankuna masu yawa, hulɗar zamantakewar jama'a da kuma iyawar tashi, duk waɗannan sun sa malam buɗe ido ya zama 'mai watsa kwayar cutar'.
A gefe guda kuma, MERS-CoV ya shiga cikin raƙuman Dromedary shekaru da yawa.
Waɗannan raƙuman sun karɓe su sosai wanda ya sa suka zama masu daidaitaccen abinci mai gina jiki na halitta.
MERS-CoV yana haifar da rashin lafiya mai sauƙi kuma yana da ƙananan ƙananan canjin canji a cikin waɗannan dabbobin.
Cutar ta zama haɗari ga ƙananan mutane, kuma mutane suna cikin ƙarshen lokacin MERS-CoV saboda kamuwa da cutar ba ta da ƙarfi.
Matsayin raƙumi a cikin watsa MERS-CoV ya bambanta da na pangolins, idan akwai, a cikin yaduwar SARS-CoV-2.
Musamman, PanGolins beta-CoV yana da yawan kamuwa da cuta a cikin PanGolins.
Suna iya zama masu karewa na ƙarshe ga SARS-CoV-2 da ke da alaƙa da beta-CoVs, kamar yadda yake a cikin yanayin SARS-CoV.
A cikin binciken da za a yi a nan gaba, za a yi la'akari ko a musanta yiwuwar yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 daga dabba zuwa mutum.
Da farko dai, jemage na iya zama masu daukar kwayar cutar SARS-CoV-2, wanda yayi kama da SARS-CoV-2.
Mutane za su iya raba wannan yanayin tare da jemage ta hanyar yanka ko kuma ta hanyar hakar ma'adinai.
Na biyu, pangolins, na iya zama ɗaya daga cikin masu haɓaka abinci mai gina jiki waɗanda aka gano kwanan nan don cutar SARS-CoV-2.
Ana samun kwayar cutar ta hanyar cin kifi da aka kashe a wurin yanka.
