WHO ta bada shawarar kada a taba idanu, hanci, ko baki ba tare da wanke hannu ba.
Yawancin magunguna kamar 62-71% ethanol, 50-100% isopropanol, 0.1% sodium hydrochlorite, 0.5% hydrogen peroxide, da 0.2-7.5% povidone-iodine suna iya kawar da gurɓataccen abu a farfajiyar (za a iya kashe ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin ƙarfe mai ƙarancin ƙarfe ta amfani da maganin kashe ƙwayoyin cuta na minti ɗaya kawai).
Sauran magungunan kamar benzalkonium da chryoxydeine ba su da tasiri sosai.
CDC ta ba da shawarar cewa idan akwai zargin ko tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a wani wuri kamar kantin sayar da abinci ko gidan yara, duk allunan, allon taɓawa, na'urorin sarrafawa ta nesa da na'urorin ATM da marasa lafiya ke amfani da su a cikin wannan yankin su kashe kwayoyin cuta.
