Amsoshin a matakin ƙasa sun haɗa da matakan sarrafa yaduwar cutar (umarnin zama a gida, umarnin zama a inda kake) da kuma dokar hana fita.Kusan mutane miliyan 300 a Amurka, ko kashi 90% na yawan jama'a, suna cikin wasu nau'ikan kullewa kamar na 2 ga Afrilu, sama da mutane miliyan 50 a Philippines, kusan mutane miliyan 59 a Afirka ta Kudu, da mutane biliyan 1.3 a Indiya.
A ranar 26 ga Maris, mutane biliyan 1.7 a duniya suna cikin wasu nau'ikan kullewa, wanda ya karu zuwa biliyan 2.6 a cikin kwanaki biyu - wanda ya kai kashi ɗaya bisa uku na yawan mutanen duniya.
An gano farkon yanayin da aka tabbatar da COVID-19 a Wuhan kafin 1 ga Disamba, 2019, tare da wani yanayin da ba a tabbatar da shi ba a ranar 17 ga Nuwamba.
Dr. Zhang Jishian ya gano tarin cututtukan cutar nimoniya da ba a san dalilin da ya sa ba a ranar 26 ga Disamba, bayan asibitin ya sanar da Wuhan Jianghan CDC a ranar 27 ga Disamba.
Gwaje-gwajen farko na kwayoyin halittar samfurin marasa lafiya na 27 ga Disamba sun nuna wanzuwar kwayar cutar coronavirus mai kama da SARS.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, Hukumar Kiwon Lafiya ta Birnin Wuhan ta fitar da wata sanarwa ga jama'a.
A ranar ne aka sanar da WHO.
A daidai lokacin da wannan sanarwar ta faru, likitoci a Wuhan sun sami gargadi daga 'yan sanda game da yada jita-jita game da barkewar cutar.
