A karshen watan Janairu, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta kaddamar da wani yunkuri na musamman wanda babban sakataren jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin, Xi Jinping, ya bayyana a matsayin "yakin mutane" don dakile yaduwar kwayar cutar.
An bayyana "babban keɓewar kai a tarihin ɗan adam" a cikin jerin tsaftacewar da aka sanar a ranar 23 ga Janairu, wanda ya kawo ƙarshen tafiya cikin gida da waje a Wuhan wanda daga baya aka faɗaɗa zuwa birane 15 na Hubei wanda ya shafi mutane miliyan 57.
An haramta amfani da motocin masu zaman kansu a cikin garin.
