An tabbatar da yaduwar COVID-19 daga China zuwa Koriya ta Kudu a ranar 20 ga Janairun 2020.
Hukumar lafiya ta kasar ta ba da rahoton karuwar adadin wadanda aka tabbatar da su a ranar 20 ga watan Fabrairu, wanda aka danganta shi da taron wani sabon addini, Shionji Church of Jesus, a garin Daegu.
An yi zargin cewa masu ibada da Shincheonji da ke ziyarar Wuhan Daegu ne suka haddasa barkewar cutar.
