A ranar 28 ga watan Fabrairu, an samu sama da mutane 2,000 da suka kamu da cutar a Koriya, wanda ya karu zuwa 3,150 a ranar 29 ga watan Fabrairu.
An killace dukkan sansanonin sojin Koriya ta Kudu bayan da aka tabbatar da cewa wasu sojoji uku sun kamu da cutar.
An kuma sauya jadawalin zirga-zirgar jiragen sama saboda tasirin hakan.Koriya ta Kudu ta ƙaddamar da shirin da aka fi sani da mafi girma a duniya don gwada yawan mutanen da ke fama da cutar, ware mutanen da ke fama da cutar, gano su, ware waɗanda suka yi hulɗa da su.
Hanyoyin gwajin sun hada da yin rajistar alamun cutar da kai ta hanyar aikace-aikacen wayar hannu, yin gwajin kwayar cutar ta hanyar tuki, wanda sakamakon sa zai kasance a rana mai zuwa, da kuma kara karfin gwajin da zai iya gwada mutane 20,000 a kowace rana.
An yi amannar cewa shirin Koriya ta Kudu ya yi nasara wajen sarrafa barkewar cutar ba tare da ware dukkan biranen ba. Da farko Shugaba Moon Jae-in ya nuna rashin amincewa da al'ummar Koriya ta Kudu a matsayin martani ga rikicin.
Yawancin 'yan Koriya sun sanya hannu kan takardun neman a tuhumi Moon ko kuma su yaba masa saboda yadda gwamnatin ta yi da cutar.
A Koriya ta Kudu, an ba da rahoton cewa mafi ƙarancin adadin masu cutar a rana ɗaya a cikin makonni huɗu ya kasance a ranar 23 ga Maris.
A ranar 29 ga watan Maris, an bayyana cewa daga ranar 1 ga watan Afrilu, duk wanda ya shigo daga kasashen waje za a killace shi na makonni biyu.
Rahotanni a ranar 1 ga Afrilu sun nuna cewa Koriya ta Kudu ta samu buƙatun taimako na gwaji daga ƙasashe 121 daban-daban.
Iran ta ba da rahoton farkon cutar SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 19 ga Fabrairu a Comm, inda ta mutu a ranar, a cewar Ma'aikatar Lafiya da Ilimin Likita.
Matakan da gwamnatin ta fara bayyana sun hada da soke kide kide da sauran al'adu, wasanni da sallar Juma'a, rufe jami'o'i, cibiyoyin ilimi da makarantu.
Iran ta kashe Riyal tiriliyan biyar don yaki da cutar.
Shugaba Hassan Rouhani ya ce a ranar 26 ga Fabrairun 2020, babu wani shiri na ware yankunan da barkewar cutar ta shafa kuma za a ware mutane ne kawai.
An sanar da tsare-tsaren iyakance zirga-zirga tsakanin biranen, amma har yanzu ana ci gaba da zirga-zirgar ababen hawa tsakanin biranen har zuwa bayan Sabuwar Shekarar Farisa.
Har zuwa ranar 16 ga watan Maris na 2020, wuraren bukukuwan Shi'a a Qom sun kasance a buɗe ga mahajjata. A watan Fabrairu, Iran ta zama cibiyar yaduwar cutar bayan China.
A yayin da ake ikirarin rufe yaduwar barkewar cutar a Iran, sama da kasashe goma sun gano cututtukansu zuwa Iran har zuwa ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, suna nuna cewa yaduwar cutar ta fi muni fiye da 388 da gwamnatin Iran ta ruwaito har zuwa wannan ranar.
An rufe majalisar dokokin Iran a ranar 3 ga watan Maris bayan da 'yan majalisa 23 daga cikin 290 suka yi gwajin cutar.
A ranar 12 ga watan Maris, Human Rights Watch ta bukaci jami'an gidan yari na Iran da su saki wadanda suka tsare a matsayin masu nuna adawa da take hakkin dan Adam ba tare da wani sharadi ba, da kuma sakin sauran fursunonin da suka cancanta.
Ya kuma ce cibiyoyin da aka rufe kamar cibiyoyin tsare mutane, inda ba a samun isassun kayayyakin kiwon lafiya, suna da haɗarin yaduwar kwayar cutar.
A ranar 15 ga watan Maris, gwamnatin Iran ta sanar da mutuwar mutane 100 a rana daya, wanda shi ne mafi girma a kasar tun lokacin da cutar ta fara bulla.
A ranar 17 ga watan Maris, akalla 'yan siyasa da jami'an gwamnati 12 na yanzu ko kuma tsoffin 'yan Iran sun mutu.
Har zuwa 23 ga Maris, Iran tana fama da sabbin cututtuka 50 a kowace awa da kuma mutuwa a kowace minti 10 sakamakon cutar.
Wani jami'in WHO ya ce Iran na iya samun adadin masu cutar da ya ninka na da aka samu sau biyar.
An kuma bayar da shawarar cewa takunkumin da Amurka ta sanya wa Iran na iya shafar karfin tattalin arzikin kasar na magance barkewar cutar.
Babban Kwamishinan kare hakkin bil adama na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya yi kira da a sassauta takunkumin tattalin arziki da aka sanya wa wasu kasashe, ciki har da Iran, wadanda cutar ta fi shafa.
An tabbatar da yaduwar cutar a Italiya a ranar 31 ga Janairu lokacin da matafiya biyu 'yan China suka gwada SARS-CoV-2 a Roma.
Sakamakon karuwar cututtukan, gwamnatin Italiya ta dakatar da dukkan jiragen da ke zuwa da dawowa daga China kuma ta ayyana dokar ta baci.
A ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, an gano wasu mutane da ba su da alaƙa da COVID-19 a Lombardy bayan an fara da tabbatar da 16 a ranar 22 ga Fabrairu, Majalisar Ministoci ta ba da sanarwar sabon dokar hana fita don shawo kan barkewar cutar, wanda ya haɗa da keɓe mutane sama da 50,000 daga birane daban-daban 11 a arewacin Italiya.
"Ba za a iya shiga ko fita daga yankin da aka yi ambaliyar ba", in ji Firayim Minista Giuseppe Conte.
"A ranar 4 ga Maris, gwamnatocin Italiya sun ba da umarnin rufe dukkan makarantu da jami'o'i gaba ɗaya saboda mutuwar 100 a Italiya".
