Mike Ryan, darektan zartarwa na shirin gaggawa na lafiya na WHO, ya yi gargadin a cikin wata sanarwa cewa lokaci ya yi da kowace gwamnati a duniya za ta yi nazarin gaskiyar.
Ya kuma yi kira ga mutane da su kasance a shirye idan cutar ta zo, kuma ya yi kira ga mutane da su kasance a shirye don yadda za su magance matsalar.
Ryan ya ci gaba da cewa bayanan da ake da su yanzu ba su ba da shawarar cewa jami'an kiwon lafiya su ayyana cutar a matsayin annoba ba, kuma ya ce yin hakan zai nuna cewa mun yarda cewa kowane mutum a duniya zai kamu da cutar.
A ranar 11 ga watan Maris, WHO ta ayyana barkewar cutar coronavirus a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
Manajan Darakta ya ce WHO tana da "babbar damuwa game da karuwar yaduwar cutar da kuma mummunan yanayin rashin aiki da rashin aiki". WHO na fuskantar suka sosai saboda nuna rashin kula da cutar ta duniya wanda ya hada da jinkirin ayyana dokar ta baci ta kiwon lafiya da kuma rarraba kwayar cutar a matsayin annoba ta duniya.
