An gaya mana mu yi kokarin yada wannan sakon ta kowane hali, kamar taron manema labarai da kuma nunawa a talabijin. Kafofin yada labarai kamar su Politico, Foreign Policy da Bloomberg sun yi ikirarin cewa kokarin tura tallafi zuwa yankunan da cutar ta addabi China wani yunkuri ne na yada mulkin duniya.
