Shugaban Iran Hassan Rouhani ya rubuta wata wasika ta jama'a ga shugabannin duniya don neman taimako a ranar 14 ga Maris, 2020, yana mai cewa kasarsa na fama da fama da barkewar cutar saboda rashin samun damar shiga kasuwannin duniya saboda takunkumin da Amurka ta sanya musu. Wannan barkewar cutar ta sa Amurka ta karɓi shirye-shiryen zamantakewar da suka zama ruwan dare a wasu ƙasashe masu arziki ciki har da kula da lafiya na duniya, kula da yara na duniya, hutun dangi masu biyan kuɗi da ƙarin kuɗi don lafiyar jama'a.
