An zargi barkewar cutar coronavirus da wasu abubuwa da dama da suka hada da karancin kayayyaki da ke tattare da karuwar amfani da kayan aikin yaki da barkewar cutar a duniya, sayayya cikin firgici da katsewar masana'antu da zirga-zirga.
Hukumar Abinci da Magunguna ta Amurka ta yi gargadin cewa akwai karancin magunguna da kayayyakin kiwon lafiya saboda karuwar bukatar masu amfani da kuma katsewar masu samar da kayayyaki.
A yankuna da dama, an ga mutane suna cin kasuwa cikin tsoro, sakamakon haka, kayan masarufi kamar abinci, takarda na bayan gida, da ruwan kwalba sun ɓace daga kayan shagon, wanda hakan ya haifar da karancin kayayyaki.
An gargadi masana'antun fasaha musamman game da jinkirin jigilar kayayyaki na lantarki.
